@startuml
actor "User" as User
participant "Web Frontend" as Frontend
participant "API Gateway\n(Kong)" as Kong
participant "Auth Service\n(Supabase)" as AuthService
database "Supabase Database" as DB
participant "Authenticator App" as AuthApp

== Luồng 1: Kích hoạt xác thực 2 lớp (2FA Enrollment) ==
User -> Frontend: Yêu cầu kích hoạt 2FA
activate Frontend

Frontend -> Kong: POST /supabase-auth-service/auth/v1/factors (TOTP)
activate Kong
Kong -> AuthService: Chuyển tiếp yêu cầu enroll
activate AuthService
AuthService -> DB: Đăng ký factor mới (status = unverified)
activate DB
DB --> AuthService: Trả về Factor ID & Secret Key
deactivate DB
AuthService --> Kong: Trả về QR Code, Secret & Factor ID
deactivate AuthService
Kong --> Frontend: Trả về QR Code, Secret & Factor ID
deactivate Kong

Frontend -> User: Hiển thị QR Code & Secret Key
User -> AuthApp: Quét mã QR / Nhập Secret Key
activate AuthApp
AuthApp --> User: Sinh mã OTP (6 chữ số)
deactivate AuthApp

User -> Frontend: Nhập mã OTP và nhấn "Xác nhận"
Frontend -> Kong: POST /supabase-auth-service/auth/v1/factors/{factorId}/challenge
activate Kong
Kong -> AuthService: Yêu cầu tạo Challenge
activate AuthService
AuthService --> Kong: Trả về Challenge ID
deactivate AuthService
Kong --> Frontend: Trả về Challenge ID
deactivate Kong

Frontend -> Kong: POST /supabase-auth-service/auth/v1/factors/{factorId}/verify
activate Kong
Kong -> AuthService: Gửi Challenge ID & mã OTP
activate AuthService
AuthService -> DB: Cập nhật trạng thái factor thành 'verified'
activate DB
DB --> AuthService: OK
deactivate DB
AuthService --> Kong: Trả về cặp token mới (AAL nâng lên aal2)
deactivate AuthService
Kong --> Frontend: Trả về cặp token mới
deactivate Kong

Frontend --> User: Kích hoạt 2FA thành công!
deactivate Frontend
@enduml
